 [!code-aspx-vb[System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource_1sql#1](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_WebNet/System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource_1sql/VB/sql1vb.aspx#1)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b4292-114">모든 뷰 상태가 저장 된 예제 페이지를 볼 때는 <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> 클래스에 `<hidden>` "__VIEWSTATE" 라는 HTML 요소입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b4292-114">When the example page is viewed, any view state is stored by the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> class in a `<hidden>` HTML element named "__VIEWSTATE".</span></span>  
  
